## Error Response Design

### Consistent Error Structure
```java
public record ErrorResponse(
    String error,
    String message,
    Instant timestamp,
    String path,
    Map<String, String> details
) {
    public static ErrorResponse of(String error, String message, String path) {
        return new ErrorResponse(
            error,
